new partnership, Mark Lair and George Steiner. A Texan and a
Washington State resident linking up. Lair's strong notrump was
met with a 2D transfer-advance-overcall from Erichsen. He lacked
the high-cards, but the seventh heart provided some security.
Steiner awaited the inevitable correction to 2H on his left,
