The E/W forcing notrump auction didn't get the job done. E/W
can make 5C (on a non-spade lead), more or less, on a double
dummy line of drawing only two rounds of trump before ruffing
the heart on dummy. Then, there is a small matter of playing
diamonds for one loser (ace and a low diamond). A 4H contract
has a chance on a non-spade lead as well. But, declarer will
lose control if the defense continually punches him with spades.
